OL,3,CThree jailed for killing of Lincoln man
OL,5,FThree people responsible for the
OL,6,Fkilling of a 46-year-old man in
OL,7,FLincoln have been sentenced to a
OL,8,Fcombined total of 21 years in prison.
OL,10,FMarc Glasscoe died following an attack
OL,11,Fat Frank Swaby Court, off Newark Road,
OL,12,Fin June.
OL,14,FEmergency services received a call
OL,15,Ffrom Lincoln County Hospital at 6.12pm
OL,16,Fon Friday 14 June to report that a man
OL,17,Fhad been brought in with serious
OL,18,Finjuries to his body and head after
OL,19,Fbeing found outside garages close to
OL,20,FFrank Swaby Court.
