OL,3,CThree jailed for killing of Lincoln man
OL,5,FOn Tuesday 26 November Lincoln Crown
OL,6,FCourt heard three men plead guilty to
OL,7,Fhis manslaughter.
OL,9,FJordan Hartley, 33, formerly of Ash
OL,10,FGrove, North Hykeham, was sentenced to
OL,11,Fseven years and six months. Jason
OL,12,FFrow, 31, formerly of Frank Swaby
OL,13,FCourt, Lincoln and Louis Giles, 33,
OL,14,Fformerly of Blackfriars Court, Lincoln
OL,15,Fwere both given sentences of six years
OL,16,Fand nine months.
