OL,3,CThree jailed for killing of Lincoln man
OL,5,FWitnesses described to police how Marc
OL,6,FGlasscoe had been dragged to nearby
OL,7,Fgarages by Louis Giles, who then left
OL,8,Fhim there. A short time later, a
OL,9,Fmember of the public called an
OL,10,Fambulance.
OL,12,FHe was taken to hospital, but died at
OL,13,F5.10pm on Sunday 16 June.
OL,15,FHis post-mortem examination showed
OL,16,Fthat he had suffered a significant
OL,17,Fbrain injury and other injuries as a
OL,18,Fresult of an assault.
