OL,3,CThree jailed for killing of Lincoln man
OL,5,FLincolnshire Police investigations
OL,6,Ffound that Mr Glasscoe had been at
OL,7,FJason Frow's address on the day he was
OL,8,Fattacked. Frow left, returning with
OL,9,FJordan Hartley and Giles. Hartley
OL,10,Fassaulted him after becoming
OL,11,Fincreasingly angry about a debt owed
OL,12,Fby someone else.
OL,14,FFrow and Giles had gone to Frow's flat
OL,15,Fwith Hartley believing the debt was
OL,16,Fgoing to be enforced with violence. Mr
OL,17,FGlasscoe was not the intended victim,
OL,18,Fbut was targeted by Hartley.
