OL,3,CThree jailed for killing of Lincoln man
OL,5,FIn a joint statement about the
OL,6,Fsentenced trio, Mr Glasscoe's family
OL,7,Fsaid: "We hope that they can use this
OL,8,Ftime in prison to turn their lives
OL,9,Faround."
OL,11,FThe lead investigator, Detective
OL,12,FInspector Andy McWatt, said: "This has
OL,13,Fbeen a very complex investigation,
OL,14,Fwith challenges right from the start
OL,15,Fin unpicking the actions and
OL,16,Fmotivations of Marc's killers.
