OL,3,CThree jailed for killing of Lincoln man
OL,5,F"As we were alerted well after the
OL,6,Fincident happened, we had to quickly
OL,7,Fmove to secure scenes and carry out
OL,8,Fforensic examinations, comb through
OL,9,Fhundreds of hours of CCTV footage,
OL,10,Ftake witness statements, door-to-door
OL,11,Fenquiries, and delve into phone data.
OL,13,F"I am glad that the three men who are
OL,14,Fresponsible for his death chose to
OL,15,Fadmit their part just before the trial
OL,16,Fbegan, saving a lengthy hearing.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
